Title: Victaulic Vic-300 MasterSeal butterfly valve 150mm
Description: Made of ductile iron, this Victaulic Vic-300 MasterSeal 165.1 x 165.1mm butterfly valve is suitable for use in pressures from vacuum to 300 psi (2065 kPa). Featuring a narrow profile disc design with a smoothly coated inner body, this valve offers excellent flow characteristics with low break-away torque, for a reduction in gear operator and actuator size and cost. The standard polyphenylene sulphide blend (PPS) coating allows for use in a variety of severe services while the dual-seal disc provides a bubble-tight seal right up to 300 psi (2065 kPa) in both directions with no added valve modifications required.

Title: VIC GRV 165.1 7890 DOUBLE REG VALVE  150
Description: Providing hydronic balance between the circuits of a system, this Victaulic 150mm double regulating and commissioning valve (DRV) also has useful pre-setting, measuring, isolating, filling and draining functions. Compatible with hot and cold water alike, this DRV works with a pre-set and centrally regulated flow rate or pressure loss for individual pipes, using a longitudinal scale for basic setting and peripheral scale for fine tuning. The DRV's presets are reproduced by opening the valve until a stop occurs. Differential pressure is measured using the valve's two threaded ports which feature useful pressure test points.
